#!/bin/bash
set -e

# Challenge 5 Setup: Skills Assessment
echo "Setting up Challenge 5: Skills Assessment..."

# Clean workspace thoroughly
cd /root/terraform-lab
terraform destroy -auto-approve 2>/dev/null || true

# Clean all workspaces
for ws in $(terraform workspace list 2>/dev/null | grep -v "default" | tr -d '*' | xargs); do
    terraform workspace select default 2>/dev/null || true
    terraform workspace delete "$ws" 2>/dev/null || true
done

# Clean files
rm -rf *
rm -rf .terraform*
rm -rf terraform.tfstate*

# Create comprehensive solution from GitHub repo
mkdir -p /root/terraform-lab-solutions/challenge-05
cp -r /root/lab-assets/assets/challenge-05/* /root/terraform-lab-solutions/challenge-05/

# Return to workspace
cd /root/terraform-lab

# Display welcome message
cat << 'EOF'

╔════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════╗
║                                                                ║
║              Challenge 5: Skills Assessment                    ║
║                                                                ║
╚════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════╝

This is your final challenge - a comprehensive assessment!

🎯 YOUR MISSION:
Build a complete multi-tier infrastructure for dev and prod environments.

📋 REQUIREMENTS:
  • Custom network
  • 3 VMs (web, app, db)
  • Variables with validation
  • Comprehensive outputs
  • Production-ready code
  • Organized file structure

⚠️  NO STEP-BY-STEP INSTRUCTIONS!
You must design and implement the solution yourself using what you've learned.

📚 RESOURCES AVAILABLE:
  • Previous challenge solutions: /root/terraform-lab-solutions/
  • Terraform documentation: terraform -help
  • Your knowledge from Challenges 1-4

💡 HINTS:
  1. Organize code into separate files (main.tf, variables.tf, locals.tf, network.tf, storage.tf, vms.tf, outputs.tf)
  2. Start with provider configuration
  3. Create network and storage resources
  4. Create VM resources
  5. Define comprehensive outputs
  6. Test with dev environment first

⏱️  TIME LIMIT: 2 hours

📁 Working Directory: /root/terraform-lab

Read the assignment carefully and plan your approach!

Good luck! You've got this! 💪

EOF

echo "Challenge 5 setup complete!"
echo ""
echo "📖 Read the full requirements in the assignment tab."
echo "🚀 When ready, start building your solution!"

